0101.name: Unknown
0101.message:
An error has occurred.

Press and hold the POWER button for at least four seconds to turn the console off.
0101.short_description: Attempted to coldboot to a title that doesn't exist.
0101.long_description: Your console is trying to boot to a title that doesn't exist, because of that the console doesn't know what to do so it will crash instead.
0101.long_solution: If you have a NAND backup for your console, restore it. If you don't, your console is bricked.
